	<paragraph>
		<heading>
			<size>1</size> Setting the assertion level 
		</heading>
		<paragraph>To modify the assertion level in a generated binary (executable or library),</paragraph>
		<list ordered="false">
			<item>Open the 
				<link>
					<url>/tools/eiffelstudio/reference/25_project_settings/10_general.xml</url>
					<label>System Settings</label>
				</link> dialog.
			</item>
			<item>In the 
				<bold>General</bold> tab, select the assertions you want to check (among require, ensure, check, loop and class invariant).
			</item>
			<item>Click 
				<bold>Apply</bold> or 
				<bold>OK</bold>.
			</item>
			<item>You must 
				<link>
					<url>10_generating_executables.xml</url>
					<label>recompile</label>
				</link> your project for the changes to take effect.
			</item>
		</list>
